  <brief_title>Implementation of a GDT Algorithm for Major Surgery Patients</brief_title>
  <official_title>Implementation and Effects of Pulse-contour-automated SVV/CI Guided Goal Directed Fluid Therapy Algorithm for the Routine Management of Major Abdominal Surgery Patients</official_title>
  <sponsors>
